{
  "texts": [
    "4 As discussed earlier, the needs of a conversation are defined by the conversational context.",
    "The requirement to be helpful to the other participant's statements, as specified by our first requirement, means tending to these needs.",
    "Furthermore, being able to respond relevantly requires correctly interpreting the conversational context.",
    "If a participant is uncertain about the meaning of the other participant's statement(s), then these needs will be unclear.",
    "In this sense, our first requirement implicitly requires that participants seek clarification in order to avoid any misunderstandings."
  ]
}